Pharmaceutical giant [[Pfizer]] came under criticism in 2001 for allegedly testing [[meningitis]] drugs on Nigerian children.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/1465532.stm | work=BBC News | title=Nigerians angered by drugs trial delay | date=July 30, 2001 | accessdate=May 4, 2010}}</ref>

